<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437954>
    dc:description "FIGURE 44. Collected specimens. Gerromorpha, Veliidae. A. Rhagovelia sooretama, apterous male from Sooretama, Espírito Santo (−19.0269, −40.2276). B. Rhagovelia tenuipes, apterous male from Sooretama, Espírito Santo (−19.0269, −40.2276). C, D. Rhagovelia teresa, apterous male and female, respectively, from Santa Teresa, Espírito Santo (−19.8967, −40.5236). Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437954/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437958>
    dc:description "FIGURE 45. Distribution in southeastern Brazil and adjacent areas. A. Rhagovelia sooretama. B. Rhagovelia tenuipes. C. Rhagovelia teresa. Stars indicate new records; circles indicate previous records." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437958/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

